*     fileinfo.sno - Count characters and lines read from stdin.
*     Tests: SIZE(), integer accumulation, unanchored loop, END branch on EOF.

         &TRIM    =  1
NEXTL    CHARS    =  CHARS + SIZE(INPUT)                    :F(DONE)
         LINES    =  LINES + 1                              :(NEXTL)
DONE     OUTPUT   =  CHARS ' characters, ' LINES ' lines read'
END
